    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div
        class="container-1 md:py-24 py-14"
      >
        <div class="flex xl:flex-row flex-col mb-24">
          <div class="xl:w-1/2 w-full mb-10 xl:mb-0">
            <div class="head-txt">
            <h6
              class=""
            >
            Get your hands on the best-quality
          </h6>
              <h2 class="max-w-[520px]">
              Bitumen, Bitumen Emulsion, Base Oil, and Fuel Oil Products from
              Mignesh Global.
            </h2>
          </div>
            <p class="xl:w-3/4 w-full text-base tracking-[0.16px]">
              Robust Infrastructure is at the core of Mignesh Global to deliver
              best-in-class high-quality end products to our clients. We have a
              full-fledged infrastructure facility to ensure seamless storage,
              supply and management of all the products, such as Bitumen,
              Bitumen Emulsion, Base Oil and Fuel Oil.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="lg:flex-grow xl:w-1/2 w-full xl:pl-8 pl-0 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center"
          >
            <Image
              alt="infra-details"
              src={infra_detail}
              class="object-cover object-center rounded"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:text-start text-center w-full lg:mb-16 mb-10"
        >
          <h1
            class="xl:text-3xl lg:text-2xl text-xl font-medium title-font text-[#48389C] xl:w-3/4 lg:w-5/6 w-full"
          >
            Our Infrastructure is a testament to our commitment to delivering
            top-notch products and services efficiently and effectively.
          </h1>
        </div>
        

        <div class="flex flex-wrap">
          <Infra_Card
            title="Manufacturing Plant Facility"
            data="We have set up our very own manufacturing plant in Baroda to ensure quick, seamless and high-quality manufacturing of diverse products."
            img={manufacturing}
          />

          <Infra_Card
            title="State-of-the-art storage facility"
            data="Mignesh Global has a huge storage facility with a capacity of 5000 metric tons, enabling us to stockpile a wide range of products in large quantities."
            img={storing}
          />

          <Infra_Card
            title="Lubricant material manufacturing"
            data="We even have a lubricant material manufacturing facility, which strengthens our capabilities to cater to the lubricant industry's diverse needs."
            img={lubricant}
          />

          <Infra_Card
            title="Availability of necessary equipment"
            data="To ensure timely and seamless delivery of products, we maintain a dedicated fleet of 8 trucks and other required equipment."
            img={equipment}
          />

          <Infra_Card
            title="Strategic presence across the country"
            data="Mignesh Global has established a strategic presence across various ports, providing us with excellent accessibility to multiple regions."
            img={strategic}
          />

          <Infra_Card
            title="Our own Logistics Company"
            data="To ensure faster and more efficient delivery of all the required products, such as Bitumen, Bitumen Emulsion, Base Oil & Fuel Oil, we have set up our own Logistics company(Mignesh Logistics)."
            img={logistics}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- infrastructure-Workflow -->

    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-[#F9F9FB]">
      <div
        class="container w-[90%] sm:max-w-lg md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl xl:max-w-6xl 2xl:max-w-7xl m-auto flex xl:px-28 px-0 md:py-24 py-14 md:flex-row flex-col items-center"
      >
        <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full mb-10 md:mb-0">
          <Image
            alt="hero"
            src={infra_workflow}
            class="object-cover object-center rounded"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 w-full lg:pl-24 md:pl-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center"
        >
          <div>
            <p class="mb-8 text-base tracking-[0.16px]">
              Mignesh Globalâ€™s Infrastructure has been strategically designed to
              enhance efficiency and reliability in all aspects of our
              operations. From production to storage and distribution, we have
              highly optimized our processes to deliver exceptional service
              consistently.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-semibold sm:text-xl text-lg mb-8 text-[#2E2D6F] tracking-[0.2px]"
            >
              Delivering a Diverse Range of High-quality Products with our
              Robust Infrastructure and experienced team.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-full md:justify-start justify-center items-end">
            <button
              class="inline-flex sm:text-xl text-base text-white bg-[#E98135] border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-indigo-600 rounded text-lg uppercase"
              ><a href="#" class="flex flex-row"
                ><span> Contact Now!</span>
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="9"
                  height="13"
                  viewBox="0 0 9 13"
                  fill="none"
                  class="ml-10 my-2"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M1.917 12.009L0 10.122L4.182 6.005L0 1.887L1.917 0L8.014 6.005L1.917 12.009Z"
                    fill="white"></path>
                </svg></a
              ></button
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
